17
00:03:01,025 --> 00:03:01,945
No.

18
00:03:07,825 --> 00:03:09,305
My classmate drank it.

19
00:03:10,505 --> 00:03:12,065
She threw away the bottle too.

20
00:03:12,825 --> 00:03:15,145
It was pointless to keep it anyway.

21
00:03:18,705 --> 00:03:20,385
You should've told me

22
00:03:20,465 --> 00:03:22,065
