23
00:03:22,145 --> 00:03:23,585
I didn't drink it anyway.

24
00:03:24,265 --> 00:03:25,665
I'll take note of it next time.

25
00:03:26,225 --> 00:03:28,145
I was careless today.

26
00:03:28,705 --> 00:03:30,265
Remember to check

27
00:03:30,345 --> 00:03:31,905
