29
00:03:39,785 --> 00:03:41,025
I'll take you back to your dorm.

30
00:03:43,225 --> 00:03:44,065
Let's go.

31
00:03:53,345 --> 00:03:55,185
Stop scratching.

32
00:03:55,265 --> 00:03:56,705
It will only get worse.

33
00:03:56,785 --> 00:03:57,945
You will get rashes again.

34
00:03:58,025 --> 00:04:00,505
I'm not scratching. I just feel hot.

35
00:04:09,305 --> 00:04:10,185
Be a good girl.

36
00:04:14,505 --> 00:04:15,385
Let's go.

37
00:04:28,625 --> 00:04:29,465
What's so funny?

38
00:04:31,345 --> 00:04:33,185
It's like you're walking your dog.

39
00:04:36,385 --> 00:04:37,225
Yes.

40
00:04:37,905 --> 00:04:39,345
