45
00:05:03,705 --> 00:05:04,625
In the past,

46
00:05:07,345 --> 00:05:08,945
didn't you always tell other people

47
00:05:09,905 --> 00:05:11,025
that I am your sister?

48
00:05:16,625 --> 00:05:18,185
