49
00:05:31,145 --> 00:05:32,065
Sang Zhi.

50
00:05:49,025 --> 00:05:49,945
It's nothing.

51
00:05:50,545 --> 00:05:51,385
Let's go.

52
00:06:03,105 --> 00:06:04,785
Your birthday is coming up, right?

53
00:06:05,465 --> 00:06:07,985
