to celebrate my birthday with me?

58
00:06:26,865 --> 00:06:28,985
Our birthdays are pretty close.

59
00:06:33,305 --> 00:06:35,105
How do you plan
to celebrate your birthday?

60
00:06:37,065 --> 00:06:38,145
I'm not celebrating it.

61
00:06:39,025 --> 00:06:39,865
Why?

62
00:06:41,105 --> 00:06:43,665
It's pointless to celebrate it alone.

63
00:06:56,825 --> 00:06:59,065
CHAPTER 15, CONFESSION

64
00:06:59,145 --> 00:07:00,665
ATTRACTION

65
00:07:04,505 --> 00:07:06,105
What's the matter with Sangsang?

66
00:07:06,185 --> 00:07:07,625
She hasn't texted us yet.

67
00:07:07,705 --> 00:07:09,385
I wonder how her date went.

68
00:07:09,865 --> 00:07:11,465
You're so nosy.

69
00:07:14,305 --> 00:07:15,145
Do you have a cold?

70
00:07:16,025 --> 00:07:16,865
No.

71
00:07:17,425 --> 00:07:19,425
I have minor symptoms. This will fix it.

72
00:07:20,745 --> 00:07:21,865
You don't understand.

73
00:07:22,425 --> 00:07:23,745
It's more interesting

74
00:07:23,825 --> 00:07:25,945
to observe other people's relationships.

75
00:07:26,025 --> 00:07:27,185
Besides,

76
00:07:27,265 --> 00:07:30,225
not all crushes reciprocate your feelings.

77
00:07:30,305 --> 00:07:32,665
Moreover, this is their first date.

78
00:07:32,745 --> 00:07:33,785
Thinking back on it,

79
00:07:33,865 --> 00:07:36,425
Sangsang was afraid to even tell him
that she likes him.

80
00:07:36,505 --> 00:07:37,505
She was so passive.

81
00:07:38,665 --> 00:07:39,905
If I were in her shoes,

82
00:07:39,985 --> 00:07:41,945
I would've rushed forward

83
00:07:42,025 --> 00:07:42,865
and confessed to him.

84
00:07:42,945 --> 00:07:44,065
Who cares?

85
00:07:44,145 --> 00:07:45,305
I would chase him first.

86
00:07:45,385 --> 00:07:46,465
Sure.

87
00:07:46,545 --> 00:07:47,905
That only works on your boyfriend.

88
00:07:47,985 --> 00:07:48,945
How would you know?

89
00:07:49,505 --> 00:07:50,785
Let me ask you this then.

90
00:07:50,865 --> 00:07:52,505
What would you do if you had a crush

91
00:07:52,585 --> 00:07:53,425
on someone?

92
00:07:54,185 --> 00:07:55,305
You asked the wrong question.

93
00:07:55,385 --> 00:07:56,425
I don't have crushes.

94
00:07:56,505 --> 00:07:57,945
I either like him or I don't.

95
00:07:58,025 --> 00:07:59,985
Okay, let me rephrase my question.

96
00:08:00,065 --> 00:08:02,425
If you like someone,

97
00:08:02,505 --> 00:08:03,865
would you chase him or not?

98
00:08:03,945 --> 00:08:05,065
I wouldn't.

99
00:08:06,105 --> 00:08:07,545
Why should I chase him

100
00:08:07,625 --> 00:08:08,785
if he never gave me any hints?

101
00:08:08,865 --> 00:08:10,665
Why wouldn't you chase him?

102
00:08:10,745 --> 00:08:12,545
What if he has the same mindset as you

103
00:08:12,625 --> 00:08:13,945
and neither of you make a move?

104
00:08:14,025 --> 00:08:15,825
Neither of you will know anything.

105
00:08:15,905 --> 00:08:17,545
I'm sure you'll regret it if he gets taken

106
00:08:17,625 --> 00:08:18,545
by another girl.

107
00:08:18,625 --> 00:08:21,145
If someone else wins him over,

108
00:08:21,225 --> 00:08:22,305
that means he wasn't mine.

109
00:08:22,385 --> 00:08:23,425
There's nothing to regret.

110
00:08:23,505 --> 00:08:24,945
There are plenty of fish in the sea.

111
00:08:25,025 --> 00:08:26,065
Let me ask you this.

112
00:08:26,145 --> 00:08:28,025
If you like a guy,

113
00:08:28,505 --> 00:08:30,345
would you chase him or not?

114
00:08:30,985 --> 00:08:32,345
Would you chase him or not?

115
00:08:33,904 --> 00:08:35,305
I…

116
00:08:35,385 --> 00:08:36,784
I don't know either.

117
00:08:37,664 --> 00:08:38,705
What do you mean?

118
00:08:38,784 --> 00:08:40,264
You asked the wrong person.

119
00:08:47,225 --> 00:08:49,025
Who will join me in the library tomorrow?

120
00:08:49,105 --> 00:08:50,625
-Me.
-Me.

121
00:08:51,265 --> 00:08:53,145
I'll ask Sangsang to join us tomorrow.

122
00:08:53,225 --> 00:08:54,065
Okay.

123
00:08:58,225 --> 00:09:00,025
We already finished supper for some time.

124
00:09:00,705 --> 00:09:01,985
Why isn't Sangsang back yet?

125
00:09:03,625 --> 00:09:04,905
Don't tell me she and her crush

126
00:09:04,985 --> 00:09:06,225
went somewhere else.

127
00:09:06,305 --> 00:09:07,625
I don't think so.

128
00:09:07,705 --> 00:09:10,305
Moreover, this is their first date.

129
00:09:11,545 --> 00:09:12,425
It's so late.

130
00:09:12,505 --> 00:09:13,745
Why hasn't she returned yet?

131
00:09:14,225 --> 00:09:15,185
Call her.

132
00:09:20,745 --> 00:09:22,225
Sangsang, where are you?

133
00:09:22,305 --> 00:09:23,305
-It's late--
-Hello?

134
00:09:25,385 --> 00:09:26,305
Wait.

135
00:09:26,385 --> 00:09:27,905
What is up with the getup?

136
00:09:27,985 --> 00:09:28,945
What's wrong?

137
00:09:29,025 --> 00:09:30,185
I'm fine.

138
00:09:30,265 --> 00:09:32,225
I had an allergic reaction to milk tea.

139
00:09:32,305 --> 00:09:33,665
-Wait!
-What?

140
00:09:33,745 --> 00:09:35,225
Why did you have milk tea?

141
00:09:35,905 --> 00:09:37,545
I only took a sip.

142
00:09:38,265 --> 00:09:40,305
Look at the rashes! How are you okay?

143
00:09:40,385 --> 00:09:41,585
You went on a date

144
00:09:41,665 --> 00:09:43,065
looking like that.

145
00:09:43,145 --> 00:09:44,025
How did it go?

146
00:09:44,905 --> 00:09:46,065
How did it go?

147
00:09:50,625 --> 00:09:51,505
Was it okay?

148
00:09:53,225 --> 00:09:54,105
Wait!

149
00:09:55,345 --> 00:09:56,545
Tell me how okay it was.

150
00:09:57,745 --> 00:09:59,185
I just

151
00:09:59,825 --> 00:10:01,225
feel that…

152
00:10:01,705 --> 00:10:02,745
Tell us.

153
00:10:03,785 --> 00:10:05,225
I feel that he likes me too.

154
00:10:05,825 --> 00:10:06,865
Really?

155
00:10:06,945 --> 00:10:08,625
Does he know that you like him too?

156
00:10:08,705 --> 00:10:09,625
No.

157
00:10:09,705 --> 00:10:11,225
I've never expressed it.

158
00:10:13,345 --> 00:10:15,105
I'm sure he knows that you like him

159
00:10:15,185 --> 00:10:16,785
if he saw you smile like this.

160
00:10:18,425 --> 00:10:19,545
But Sangsang,

161
00:10:19,625 --> 00:10:20,945
you mustn't let him know

162
00:10:21,025 --> 00:10:22,585
that you still like him going forward.

163
00:10:23,145 --> 00:10:24,265
In a relationship,

164
00:10:24,345 --> 00:10:26,465
you want to be the one being pursued.

165
00:10:29,425 --> 00:10:30,505
But what if

166
00:10:31,465 --> 00:10:32,545
he doesn't pursue me?

167
00:10:32,625 --> 00:10:34,425
I don't think that will happen.

168
00:10:34,505 --> 00:10:36,345
Trust me this time.

169
00:10:36,425 --> 00:10:37,625
Trust her this time.

170
00:10:37,705 --> 00:10:38,665
It will work.

171
00:10:38,745 --> 00:10:39,625
It will be fine.

172
00:10:39,705 --> 00:10:40,705
Just trust me this time.

173
00:10:40,785 --> 00:10:41,625
I'm definitely right.

174
00:10:42,385 --> 00:10:43,265
Okay then.

175
00:10:44,265 --> 00:10:45,465
I'll wait for him to pursue me.

176
00:10:45,545 --> 00:10:46,745
That's right.

177
00:10:46,825 --> 00:10:48,185
If he doesn't pursue me,

178
00:10:49,105 --> 00:10:50,465
I'll pursue him.

179
00:10:52,345 --> 00:10:53,465
That was a waste of my time.

180
00:10:55,265 --> 00:10:56,345
You're hopeless.

181
00:10:56,945 --> 00:10:58,825
Your face! Hurry and take your medicine.

182
00:10:58,905 --> 00:11:00,025
It's so red.

183
00:11:01,505 --> 00:11:02,505
Sangsang, you can do it.

184
00:11:05,225 --> 00:11:07,865
MARCH 16TH, FRIDAY

185
00:11:07,945 --> 00:11:10,545
HE CALLED ME HIS FRIEND

186
00:11:10,625 --> 00:11:12,785
INSTEAD OF HIS LITTLE SISTER

187
00:11:15,305 --> 00:11:16,545
Are you waiting at the entrance?

188
00:11:17,065 --> 00:11:18,225
Okay.

189
00:11:18,305 --> 00:11:19,145
I'll head there.

190
00:11:38,905 --> 00:11:39,985
Sang Zhi.

191
00:11:42,865 --> 00:11:44,385
-Jiang Ming.
-Happy birthday.

192
00:11:45,185 --> 00:11:46,225
Your birthday present.

193
00:11:49,745 --> 00:11:51,865
Thank you, but I won't take it.

194
00:11:52,425 --> 00:11:53,425
I already bought it.

195
00:11:53,505 --> 00:11:54,985
I'll be in an awkward spot

196
00:11:55,065 --> 00:11:56,025
if you don't accept it.

197
00:11:56,585 --> 00:11:57,505
Just take it.

198
00:12:00,265 --> 00:12:01,825
Okay then. Thank you.

199
00:12:01,905 --> 00:12:03,785
Are you free later? Let's celebrate.

200
00:12:10,905 --> 00:12:11,785
Hello.

201
00:12:15,945 --> 00:12:17,425
I'll go then.

202
00:12:17,505 --> 00:12:18,465
Have a happy birthday.

203
00:12:19,145 --> 00:12:20,225
Thank you.

204
00:12:20,305 --> 00:12:21,145
Bye.

205
00:12:48,465 --> 00:12:49,585
I'll hold it for you.

206
00:13:02,145 --> 00:13:04,945
Is he the manly man you meant?

207
00:13:05,625 --> 00:13:06,865
I told you already.

208
00:13:06,945 --> 00:13:07,985
It's not him.

209
00:13:10,265 --> 00:13:11,185
Is that so?

210
00:13:19,025 --> 00:13:20,225
Take a look.

211
00:13:24,185 --> 00:13:25,705
Did you take a clear look?

212
00:13:25,785 --> 00:13:26,745
What are you doing?

213
00:13:28,625 --> 00:13:29,585
Look at me.

214
00:13:30,545 --> 00:13:31,985
Do I look like

215
00:13:32,825 --> 00:13:33,905
the man you described?

216
00:13:36,025 --> 00:13:37,705
What is he talking about?

217
00:13:39,385 --> 00:13:40,465
What does he mean?

218
00:13:41,505 --> 00:13:43,345
Does he know already?

219
00:13:46,625 --> 00:13:49,025
No, I cannot admit it.

220
00:13:50,705 --> 00:13:52,065
If I do,

221
00:13:52,145 --> 00:13:53,505
it would be as good as telling him

222
00:13:53,985 --> 00:13:55,545
that I've had a crush on him all along.

223
00:13:58,425 --> 00:13:59,305
No.

224
00:14:02,345 --> 00:14:03,545
Is that so?

225
00:14:10,145 --> 00:14:12,185
Jiaxu, you should

226
00:14:12,265 --> 00:14:14,145
stop mentioning him to me again.

227
00:14:14,225 --> 00:14:16,945
You told me that he is a jerk, right?

228
00:14:17,025 --> 00:14:18,465
That's why I stopped contacting him.

229
00:14:19,505 --> 00:14:20,385
Now,

230
00:14:21,465 --> 00:14:23,145
there isn't anyone I like.

231
00:14:30,625 --> 00:14:33,545
You said that he is a ladies' man.

232
00:14:34,145 --> 00:14:35,185
When did I…

233
00:14:40,025 --> 00:14:42,265
Did I tell him that that day?

234
00:14:47,385 --> 00:14:48,385
Yes, a little.

235
00:14:49,225 --> 00:14:51,345
Do you even know what that term means?

236
00:14:52,665 --> 00:14:54,065
Jiaxu, don't you know what it means?

237
00:14:56,145 --> 00:14:57,505
I told you.

238
00:14:57,585 --> 00:14:58,865
You should go online more often.

239
00:14:58,945 --> 00:15:00,465
Our generation gap is becoming obvious.

240
00:15:01,185 --> 00:15:02,385
Tell me then.

241
00:15:02,465 --> 00:15:03,745
What does the term mean?

242
00:15:05,385 --> 00:15:06,705
It means

243
00:15:08,865 --> 00:15:13,785
a guy with many female friends.

244
00:15:15,265 --> 00:15:17,465
He's nice to all women.

245
00:15:18,425 --> 00:15:20,625
And he doesn't have a girlfriend.

246
00:15:22,665 --> 00:15:24,465
If a guy fulfills
one of these three criteria,

247
00:15:24,545 --> 00:15:26,385
does that make him a ladies' man?

248
00:15:26,465 --> 00:15:28,385
Of course not. It must be all three.

249
00:15:35,305 --> 00:15:37,025
You're pretty good at framing people.

250
00:15:37,665 --> 00:15:39,025
What did you say?

251
00:15:41,825 --> 00:15:43,025
Did I say anything?

252
00:15:44,665 --> 00:15:45,985
You did just now.

253
00:15:59,025 --> 00:16:00,305
002 BOUND FOR HONGXI BUS TERMINAL

254
00:16:01,145 --> 00:16:02,505
This is strange.

255
00:16:02,585 --> 00:16:03,745
Why was the movie in theaters

256
00:16:03,825 --> 00:16:04,945
for such a short time only?

257
00:16:06,185 --> 00:16:07,585
It's all because you were too busy.

258
00:16:10,825 --> 00:16:12,225
Are you blaming me then?

259
00:16:14,705 --> 00:16:15,825
No.

260
00:16:16,385 --> 00:16:17,585
This is pretty good too.

261
00:16:17,665 --> 00:16:19,185
The theater downtown

262
00:16:19,265 --> 00:16:21,025
