263
00:16:21,105 --> 00:16:22,625
And it's your birthday.

264
00:16:23,465 --> 00:16:24,865
That makes it more meaningful.

265
00:16:49,185 --> 00:16:50,025
Hold onto me

266
00:16:50,105 --> 00:16:51,065
so you don't fall.

267
00:17:09,184 --> 00:17:10,025
Hold tight.

268
00:18:05,105 --> 00:18:06,905
You want to get a drink again, don't you?

269
00:18:06,985 --> 00:18:08,425
You're not having any anyway.

270
00:18:09,505 --> 00:18:11,745
Aren't you afraid of blushing again?

271
00:18:13,625 --> 00:18:15,625
It was an allergic reaction,

272
00:18:15,705 --> 00:18:16,865
not blushing.

273
00:18:18,425 --> 00:18:20,105
-Hi. What would you like to order?
-Hello.

274
00:18:20,865 --> 00:18:23,825
A girl with square glasses works here.

275
00:18:23,905 --> 00:18:25,105
Is she here today?

276
00:18:25,185 --> 00:18:28,505
-She's on the night shift today.
-I want lemon tea with boba.

277
00:18:28,585 --> 00:18:29,425
Okay. Hot or iced?

278
00:18:29,505 --> 00:18:30,345
Iced.

279
00:18:30,425 --> 00:18:31,585
Hot.

280
00:18:32,305 --> 00:18:33,425
Make it hot.

281
00:18:33,505 --> 00:18:35,105
It's too cold for iced beverages.

282
00:18:35,185 --> 00:18:36,665
I want it iced.

283
00:18:36,745 --> 00:18:37,585
Okay.

284
00:18:37,665 --> 00:18:38,905
It's stuffy in the theater.

285
00:18:40,025 --> 00:18:41,825
Iced lemon tea with boba.

