00:18:41,905 --> 00:18:44,145
Fine, you can have it.

287
00:18:44,625 --> 00:18:46,185
-Here.
-I'll scan your phone.

288
00:18:47,225 --> 00:18:48,745
It will be cold in the theater later.

289
00:18:48,825 --> 00:18:50,305
The air-conditioning is strong.

290
00:18:50,385 --> 00:18:51,545
Don't drink too much.

291
00:18:52,625 --> 00:18:53,945
Mind your own business.

292
00:18:54,505 --> 00:18:55,945
Do you find me annoying?

293
00:18:56,025 --> 00:18:57,225
No.

294
00:18:57,305 --> 00:18:58,665
Wasn't that what you meant?

295
00:18:59,465 --> 00:19:00,385
No.

296
00:19:02,225 --> 00:19:03,225
You should get used to it.

297
00:19:09,505 --> 00:19:10,505
Thank you.

298
00:19:14,665 --> 00:19:15,545
Have a good day.

299
00:19:23,465 --> 00:19:24,385
Over there.

300
00:19:47,425 --> 00:19:48,665
I'll hold it for you.

301
00:19:53,385 --> 00:19:54,625
Do you want to drink it?

302
00:20:01,225 --> 00:20:02,625
I can hold it myself.

303
00:20:03,185 --> 00:20:04,425
You…

304
00:20:05,225 --> 00:20:07,185
You can drink your drink.

305
00:20:07,265 --> 00:20:08,705
Why did you touch my hand on purpose?

306
00:20:20,625 --> 00:20:22,865
I can actually hold it myself.

307
00:20:22,945 --> 00:20:24,225
Aren't you afraid of cold hands?

308
00:20:25,185 --> 00:20:26,825
Won't you get cold hands too?

309
00:20:29,785 --> 00:20:30,625
You're right.

310
00:20:33,265 --> 00:20:34,745
You can warm it up for me.

311
00:20:44,505 --> 00:20:45,545
I don't think

312
00:20:46,985 --> 00:20:47,825
it is

313
00:20:49,385 --> 00:20:50,985
appropriate

314
00:20:51,825 --> 00:20:52,985
for us to do that.

315
00:20:59,625 --> 00:21:01,545
You're right.

316
00:21:05,145 --> 00:21:06,745
After all, we haven't put a label on it.

317
00:21:09,025 --> 00:21:09,945
Label?

318
00:21:31,905 --> 00:21:32,785
Here you go.

319
00:21:32,865 --> 00:21:33,745
Wipe your hands.

320
00:21:51,625 --> 00:21:52,465
Hold it.

321
00:22:28,465 --> 00:22:29,385
-Zhizhi.
-Jiaxu.

322
00:22:32,225 --> 00:22:33,065
You first.

323
00:22:34,865 --> 00:22:35,705
It's nothing.

324
00:22:35,785 --> 00:22:37,705
I just want to ask you
where we're going later.

325
00:22:38,465 --> 00:22:39,665
Let's go

326
00:22:39,745 --> 00:22:40,785
to my place later.

327
00:22:45,865 --> 00:22:47,865
My gift for you is at my place.

328
00:22:47,945 --> 00:22:49,145
And then,

329
00:22:49,225 --> 00:22:50,865
we can eat some cake together.

330
00:22:54,705 --> 00:22:55,585
Jiaxu.

331
00:22:56,985 --> 00:22:58,425
Do you want me to go to your place?

332
00:23:02,905 --> 00:23:04,825
Didn't you tell me before

333
00:23:04,905 --> 00:23:07,185
not to visit you at your place or office?

334
00:23:08,185 --> 00:23:09,865
When did I say something like that?

335
00:23:12,385 --> 00:23:13,545
That time

336
00:23:13,625 --> 00:23:15,385
when I brought you the peephole camera.

337
00:23:15,945 --> 00:23:17,905
You pulled me off to one side and told me

338
00:23:17,985 --> 00:23:20,745
not to visit you
at your place or office again.

339
00:23:24,345 --> 00:23:25,305
That time?

340
00:23:27,745 --> 00:23:29,025
It's like this.

341
00:23:29,105 --> 00:23:29,985
Jiang Ying

342
00:23:30,065 --> 00:23:31,665
suddenly came to find me at my office.

343
00:23:32,225 --> 00:23:34,065
I was afraid she might hurt you

344
00:23:34,145 --> 00:23:35,985
if she saw you.

345
00:23:36,065 --> 00:23:37,145
That's why…

346
00:23:39,825 --> 00:23:40,745
But it's true.

347
00:23:40,825 --> 00:23:42,225
I was too hasty that day.

348
00:23:42,305 --> 00:23:43,865
I may not have made myself clear.

349
00:23:50,465 --> 00:23:53,545
So you've been upset lately

350
00:23:54,185 --> 00:23:55,505
because of this?

351
00:24:04,905 --> 00:24:06,425
You're making it sound

352
00:24:07,305 --> 00:24:09,425
as if I'm a petty person.

353
00:24:12,065 --> 00:24:12,985
No.

354
00:24:13,065 --> 00:24:15,225
This was indeed my fault.

355
00:24:15,785 --> 00:24:17,785
I should've explained it to you clearly.

356
00:24:17,865 --> 00:24:19,985
Let me apologize to you.

357
00:24:30,185 --> 00:24:31,225
I guess

358
00:24:31,785 --> 00:24:34,025
I was being a bit petty too.

359
00:24:35,625 --> 00:24:36,585
I apologize to you too.

360
00:24:37,225 --> 00:24:38,145
I'm sorry.

361
00:24:40,145 --> 00:24:42,025
So now, the misunderstanding is resolved.

362
00:24:42,865 --> 00:24:43,745
Let's go eat cake.

363
00:24:45,705 --> 00:24:46,745
Let's go.

364
00:25:07,865 --> 00:25:08,905
I prepared these for you.

365
00:25:10,745 --> 00:25:11,785
For me?

366
00:25:15,225 --> 00:25:16,145
They are pretty nice.

367
00:25:19,705 --> 00:25:20,785
Don't change into them yet.

368
00:25:21,865 --> 00:25:23,705
You haven't been to the rooftop, right?

369
00:25:23,785 --> 00:25:24,745
Go and check it out.

370
00:26:07,465 --> 00:26:09,145
Why are there two cakes?

371
00:26:10,185 --> 00:26:11,585
I made one of them.

372
00:26:11,665 --> 00:26:12,825
It doesn't contain any dairy,

373
00:26:12,905 --> 00:26:13,865
so you can eat it.

374
00:26:16,345 --> 00:26:17,825
It's this one, right?

375
00:26:19,585 --> 00:26:21,065
Can you tell?

376
00:26:21,145 --> 00:26:22,025
It's pretty obvious.

377
00:26:22,905 --> 00:26:25,225
So why did you also buy this one?

378
00:26:26,025 --> 00:26:27,785
I was afraid mine would turn out ugly,

379
00:26:27,865 --> 00:26:29,865
so I bought another one
to stick your candles in.

380
00:26:31,065 --> 00:26:32,665
It's not ugly. It looks great.

381
00:26:32,745 --> 00:26:33,625
Is that so?

382
00:26:34,625 --> 00:26:36,665
Then pick one to stick your candles in.

383
00:26:38,145 --> 00:26:40,305
Then I'll go

384
00:26:41,305 --> 00:26:42,225
with this one.

385
00:26:46,545 --> 00:26:47,505
Okay.

386
00:26:50,825 --> 00:26:52,225
How many candles do you want?

387
00:26:52,305 --> 00:26:53,585
One is enough.

388
00:26:53,665 --> 00:26:54,545
-This one--
-No way.

389
00:26:56,225 --> 00:26:57,265
You need 19 candles.

390
00:26:57,825 --> 00:26:59,465
You need to know your own age.

391
00:27:03,905 --> 00:27:04,785
Jiaxu.

392
00:27:05,745 --> 00:27:07,505
If we have to know our own age

393
00:27:08,025 --> 00:27:09,345
when we celebrate our birthdays,

394
00:27:09,425 --> 00:27:10,665
I don't think

395
00:27:10,745 --> 00:27:12,745
there will be enough candles for you.

396
00:27:18,265 --> 00:27:19,945
You just have to mock my age every day.

397
00:27:47,945 --> 00:27:50,025
Happy birthday to you

398
00:27:50,625 --> 00:27:52,945
Happy birthday to you

399
00:27:53,025 --> 00:27:56,025
Happy birthday to you

400
00:27:56,105 --> 00:27:57,945
Happy birthday to you

401
00:27:59,985 --> 00:28:02,025
This is the first birthday

402
00:28:02,105 --> 00:28:03,825
that I'm spending with Jiaxu.

403
00:28:04,465 --> 00:28:05,465
I hope

404
00:28:05,545 --> 00:28:07,345
there will be many more to come.

405
00:28:10,105 --> 00:28:11,105
Make a wish.

406
00:28:14,625 --> 00:28:15,825
Can I say it out loud?

407
00:28:16,985 --> 00:28:18,065
Do you want to?

408
00:28:36,225 --> 00:28:37,305
Happy birthday!

409
00:28:40,865 --> 00:28:41,705
Cut the cake.

410
00:28:43,145 --> 00:28:44,785
Make the first cut.

411
00:28:46,505 --> 00:28:47,385
Okay.

412
00:29:04,505 --> 00:29:05,505
Here.

413
00:29:06,665 --> 00:29:08,745
Sang Zhi, you're officially 19 years old.

414
00:29:09,505 --> 00:29:11,265
Try it. See if it tastes good.

415
00:29:22,905 --> 00:29:23,825
Does it taste good?

416
00:29:24,785 --> 00:29:25,665
It's delicious.

417
00:29:25,745 --> 00:29:27,585
It's just the same as that one. Delicious.

418
00:29:28,625 --> 00:29:29,505
Great.

419
00:29:31,745 --> 00:29:32,705
Your birthday present.

420
00:29:36,345 --> 00:29:37,705
You already made a cake for me.

421
00:29:37,785 --> 00:29:38,705
Do I get a gift too?

422
00:29:38,785 --> 00:29:41,545
The cake will only last for a while.

423
00:29:41,625 --> 00:29:43,465
A present should last longer.

424
00:29:44,545 --> 00:29:45,705
Thank you, Jiaxu.

425
00:29:49,785 --> 00:29:52,225
You can open it when you get back.

426
00:29:54,785 --> 00:29:55,745
Okay.

427
00:29:58,185 --> 00:29:59,385
I'll try a slice too.

428
00:30:24,785 --> 00:30:26,305
Did someone give that to you?

429
00:30:26,905 --> 00:30:27,985
Aren't you going to open it?

430
00:30:30,145 --> 00:30:31,265
I'll do it when I get back.

431
00:30:34,225 --> 00:30:35,625
Is that guy trying to pursue you?

432
00:30:38,425 --> 00:30:40,465
It looks like you're pretty popular.

433
00:30:48,105 --> 00:30:49,425
So can you tell me

434
00:30:50,225 --> 00:30:51,545
what it takes

435
00:30:52,385 --> 00:30:53,465
for a guy to pursue you?

436
00:30:59,025 --> 00:31:00,745
What? That's nonsense.

437
00:31:02,905 --> 00:31:04,105
Then tell me.

438
00:31:04,865 --> 00:31:06,585
What do you look for

439
00:31:07,345 --> 00:31:08,345
in a guy?

440
00:31:16,505 --> 00:31:17,505
He must be handsome,

441
00:31:20,505 --> 00:31:21,425
have a good temper,

442
00:31:23,705 --> 00:31:24,625
and…

443
00:31:29,225 --> 00:31:30,625
He must be a head taller than me.

444
00:31:32,585 --> 00:31:33,865
Anything else?

445
00:31:34,985 --> 00:31:36,305
And…

446
00:31:37,665 --> 00:31:39,305
He must have morals. That's all.

447
00:31:39,865 --> 00:31:40,745
Is that all?

448
00:31:49,425 --> 00:31:50,385
I think

449
00:31:51,465 --> 00:31:53,985
I check all these boxes.

450
00:31:57,025 --> 00:31:58,345
So I want to ask you something.

451
00:32:05,945 --> 00:32:07,185
Can I pursue you?

452
00:32:29,745 --> 00:32:30,625
I…

453
00:32:32,785 --> 00:32:33,705
I…

454
00:32:34,305 --> 00:32:35,265
Jiaxu.

455
00:32:36,625 --> 00:32:38,905
Does what you said

456
00:32:40,145 --> 00:32:43,745
mean the same as what I think it means?

457
00:32:45,145 --> 00:32:47,225
Is there another meaning to it?

458
00:32:51,625 --> 00:32:53,145
But didn't you say

459
00:32:54,865 --> 00:32:56,025
that I'm a kiddo?

460
00:32:57,185 --> 00:32:58,505
You think I'm too young.

461
00:32:59,905 --> 00:33:01,625
That is just a nickname.

462
00:33:01,705 --> 00:33:02,945
If you like it,

463
00:33:03,025 --> 00:33:04,985
I can call you that even when you're 80.

464
00:33:06,505 --> 00:33:07,345
Besides,

465
00:33:08,025 --> 00:33:09,865
you call me your brother all the time.

466
00:33:09,945 --> 00:33:11,665
Do you really consider me your brother?

467
00:33:14,305 --> 00:33:15,745
I do consider you my brother.

468
00:33:18,825 --> 00:33:19,705
But

469
00:33:20,585 --> 00:33:22,625
I don't want to be just your brother.

470
00:33:23,705 --> 00:33:25,305
I want to be your boyfriend.

471
00:33:48,265 --> 00:33:49,745
Say something.

472
00:33:50,305 --> 00:33:51,385
If you don't say something,

473
00:33:52,745 --> 00:33:54,225
I don't think I can breathe.

474
00:33:56,185 --> 00:33:57,305
You can't breathe?

475
00:33:58,705 --> 00:33:59,825
More like

476
00:34:00,625 --> 00:34:02,025
I can't breathe.

477
00:34:06,625 --> 00:34:07,585
Jiaxu.

478
00:34:08,824 --> 00:34:10,145
No one asks for permission

479
00:34:10,225 --> 00:34:12,425
before pursuing someone.

480
00:34:13,784 --> 00:34:16,025
I have to make myself clear.

481
00:34:16,784 --> 00:34:18,824
Otherwise, what will I do
if you think I'm good to you

482
00:34:18,905 --> 00:34:20,545
because I'm your elder?

483
00:34:21,744 --> 00:34:23,264
That's your business.

484
00:34:23,344 --> 00:34:25,025
It has nothing to do with me.

485
00:34:28,344 --> 00:34:29,705
Why don't you just tell me?

486
00:34:30,585 --> 00:34:31,585
Tell me

487
00:34:32,065 --> 00:34:34,385
if you feel that way about me.

488
00:34:41,824 --> 00:34:42,665
No.

489
00:34:45,385 --> 00:34:46,264
However,

490
00:34:47,705 --> 00:34:49,304
what I mean is

491
00:34:50,185 --> 00:34:51,465
that I won't know

492
00:34:52,225 --> 00:34:54,025
if I feel that way about you

493
00:34:54,625 --> 00:34:55,985
until you pursue me.

494
00:35:02,425 --> 00:35:03,265
Sure.

495
00:35:04,825 --> 00:35:07,585
Then can you give me a hint first?

496
00:35:08,145 --> 00:35:10,025
How long do I need to pursue you?

497
00:35:11,105 --> 00:35:12,465
How can I give you a hint?

498
00:35:13,025 --> 00:35:15,145
You make it sound
as if I'll say yes for sure.

499
00:35:16,425 --> 00:35:17,305
How could you say no?

500
00:35:17,385 --> 00:35:18,625
You won't win me over.

501
00:35:18,705 --> 00:35:19,545
I'm tough to please.

502
00:35:20,865 --> 00:35:22,025
Fine.

503
00:35:22,105 --> 00:35:23,465
Then I'll drag it out.

504
00:35:24,025 --> 00:35:25,585
I'll pursue you for a decade or so.

505
00:35:27,625 --> 00:35:30,905
But if you go and meet other guys,

506
00:35:30,985 --> 00:35:33,265
I'll complain to your parents.

507
00:35:35,705 --> 00:35:37,145
Why would you complain to them?

508
00:35:37,745 --> 00:35:39,265
Did you forget the time

509
00:35:39,345 --> 00:35:41,265
when I met your teacher as your guardian?

510
00:35:43,225 --> 00:35:44,545
That was ages ago.

511
00:35:44,625 --> 00:35:45,665
Why are you bringing it up?

512
00:35:46,745 --> 00:35:48,105
I'm a nostalgic person.

513
00:35:50,105 --> 00:35:50,945
By the way,

514
00:35:51,465 --> 00:35:52,945
I forgot to tell you this.

515
00:35:53,025 --> 00:35:55,385
You look pretty today.

516
00:36:03,385 --> 00:36:04,305
I know.

517
00:36:06,265 --> 00:36:07,945
You dressed up to see me.

518
00:36:08,545 --> 00:36:10,105
Then you say you have no feelings for me.

519
00:36:11,785 --> 00:36:13,785
Can't I make myself pretty on my birthday?

520
00:36:14,465 --> 00:36:17,025
Did you think I dressed up for you?

521
00:36:17,105 --> 00:36:18,225
Fine.

522
00:36:18,305 --> 00:36:20,025
I know you don't have feelings for me.

523
00:36:20,105 --> 00:36:21,385
Can't I imagine things

524
00:36:21,465 --> 00:36:22,465
and make myself happy?

525
00:36:22,545 --> 00:36:24,225
Then keep it to yourself.

526
00:36:24,785 --> 00:36:26,185
I want to say it out loud,

527
00:36:26,265 --> 00:36:27,385
so that you know.

528
00:36:41,305 --> 00:36:42,545
By the way, Jiaxu.

529
00:36:44,745 --> 00:36:45,785
You…

530
00:36:46,905 --> 00:36:48,345
You didn't

531
00:36:48,425 --> 00:36:49,785
confess to me today, right?

532
00:36:50,265 --> 00:36:51,305
You only asked me

533
00:36:51,385 --> 00:36:52,505
whether you could pursue me.

534
00:36:52,985 --> 00:36:54,745
I technically didn't reject you,

535
00:36:54,825 --> 00:36:55,785
right?

536
00:36:56,345 --> 00:36:57,745
So then,

537
00:36:57,825 --> 00:36:59,065
can I take the cake with me?

538
00:37:03,465 --> 00:37:04,345
Then

539
00:37:05,145 --> 00:37:06,785
are you saying

540
00:37:07,505 --> 00:37:09,425
that I confess to you right now,

541
00:37:09,505 --> 00:37:11,265
-you will say yes?
-No.

542
00:37:11,345 --> 00:37:12,665
Then you can't take it.

543
00:37:13,985 --> 00:37:15,425
You can keep this one.

544
00:37:15,505 --> 00:37:17,745
I'll take this one, all right?

545
00:37:17,825 --> 00:37:18,705
No.

546
00:37:18,785 --> 00:37:20,825
Why are you so petty?

547
00:37:20,905 --> 00:37:22,025
I'm just saying

548
00:37:22,105 --> 00:37:23,625
that you can pursue me a little more.

549
00:37:23,705 --> 00:37:24,825
It's not like I didn't agree…

550
00:37:29,505 --> 00:37:30,545
I…

551
00:37:30,625 --> 00:37:31,945
You have to pursue me first

552
00:37:32,705 --> 00:37:33,825
before I can know

553
00:37:33,905 --> 00:37:35,865
if I feel that way about you.

554
00:37:36,665 --> 00:37:37,585
Do you understand?

555
00:37:38,865 --> 00:37:39,985
Fine.

556
00:37:40,545 --> 00:37:41,945
That's okay.

557
00:37:42,025 --> 00:37:43,425
If you don't feel that way about me,

558
00:37:43,505 --> 00:37:45,025
I'll keep pursuing you.

559
00:37:47,625 --> 00:37:48,745
Eat the cake.

560
00:37:52,225 --> 00:37:53,985
Sit down and enjoy it.

561
00:38:01,505 --> 00:38:03,265
You can take the cake with you.

562
00:38:07,785 --> 00:38:08,865
Both of them?

563
00:38:11,225 --> 00:38:12,105
If you like it,

564
00:38:12,585 --> 00:38:14,425
I can make it for you every day.

565
00:38:20,585 --> 00:38:21,465
Sure.

566
00:38:41,505 --> 00:38:42,585
I'm back!

567
00:38:48,265 --> 00:38:49,425
Are you guys asleep?

568
00:38:51,105 --> 00:38:51,945
It's pretty early.

569
00:39:00,225 --> 00:39:01,865
I'm back.

570
